  "description": "Howdy folk. Let me start this by expressing my gratitude that you\u0026rsquo;re reading it, and that you\u0026rsquo;ve subscribed to it, if you have. If you haven’t: (If you\u0026rsquo;re getting this and don\u0026rsquo;t remember signing up for it: you\u0026rsquo;re an active donor to my Liberapay or Patreon so I transferred you.)\nSecond, please forgive any issues these newsletters might have early on - I\u0026rsquo;ve never used Substack before, and I\u0026rsquo;m sure I\u0026rsquo;ll click the wrong button at least once!\n",
